quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Ne balia abalasuubilanga okhubukanana ninafu baboola mbu: “Shichila shina nibalakhwishilia Malaika nohomba khulole Nyasaye wefu Omulesi?” Bakhola obufuru mumioyo chiabu mana nibaloba okhuloba okhukhongo."
  25,22,"Inyanga yabalilola Abamalaika, Aboononi shibaliba nende obusangafu inyanga eyo tawe, ne baliboola mbu: “Khure ehale nende eshinyasio shiakhulenjelekhwo shino.”"
  25,23,"Ne khulirera koosi kalia akabakhola mubikhole mana khukakhole shinga olufu lutumulilwe."
  25,24,"Abandu bomumukunda kwomwikulu inyanga eyo baliba mushimenyo eshilayi nende habundu halayi muno wokhuwulushila."
  25,25,"Ne inyanga yelikulu liliatikha, mana lirere amaleesi amanji, ne Abamalaika balishibwa mubunji."
  25,26,"Obwami bwatoto inyanga eyo buliba obwa Omunji wetsimbabaasi, ne iliba inyanga indinyu khubakhayi."
  25,27,"Ne inyanga eyo owobubii aliiluma amakhono kaye naboola mbu: “Emanyangakhwo, ndakhabukule injila halala nende Omurumwa."
  25,28,"Abayiee! Emanyangakho sindakhabukule lebe okhuba omwitsa wanje wa mbusia ngonia tawe."
  25,29,"Toto ye yangosia ndalekha okhuloonda ameetsulisio nikamalile okhunzulila.” Ne toto Shetani asukunanga muno Omundu."
  25,30,"Ne Omurumwa yaboolanga mbu: “Ewe Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto Abandu banje bakhola Ikurani ino okhuba shinga likubili.”"
  25,31,"Ni endiosa nilwa khwakholela buli Omurumwa omusuku okhurula mubandu ababii. Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi ayela okhuba Omulunjisia nende Omukhoonyi muno."
  25,32,"Ne Abakhayi nibaboola mbu: “Mana bane naleeshilibwa Ikurani yoosi lulala butswa.” Ni endio kho khunyoole okhutinyisia omwoyo kukwo, ne khwayihelasia obulayi."